  <brief_title>Comparison Between Two Analgesic Methods for Pain Relief Following Surgical Abortion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison Between Two Analgesic Methods for Pain Relief Following Surgical Abortion</official_title>
  <sponsors>
